post.description:
Retrieve episodes by business data in canvas context.

POST /api/episodes/retrieve/business-data
{
    "agent_id": "agent_123",
    "filters": {
        "approval_status": "approved",
        "revenue": {"$gt": 1000000}
    },
    "limit": 10
}

Returns:
    Episodes matching business data filters

Examples:
    Find $1M+ approved workflows:
    {
        "agent_id": "agent_123",
        "filters": {
            "approval_status": "approved",
            "revenue": {"$gt": 1000000}
        }
    }
